@startuml Sequence_Bastion_Access
!theme plain

title Bastion Access & Network Enumeration

actor "Workshop\nParticipant" as user
participant "Fail2Ban" as f2b
participant "UFW Firewall" as ufw
participant "Bastion\n10.10.1.30" as bastion
participant "Juice Shop\n10.10.1.20" as juice
participant "Internal API\n10.10.2.20" as api
participant "MySQL\n10.10.3.20" as db
participant "OpenLDAP\n10.10.3.30" as ldap

== SSH Login ==

user -> ufw : SSH to vps-ip:2222
activate ufw
ufw -> f2b : Check rate limit
activate f2b
f2b --> ufw : Allow (< 10 attempts)
deactivate f2b
ufw -> bastion : Forward SSH
activate bastion
bastion --> user : Password prompt
user -> bastion : analyst / analyst123
note over bastion : [VULN] Password auth enabled\nShould be key-only
bastion --> user : Shell access
deactivate bastion
deactivate ufw

== Network Enumeration from Bastion ==

user -> bastion : nmap -sn 10.10.1.0/24 10.10.2.0/24 10.10.3.0/24
activate bastion
note over bastion : [VULN] Bastion connected to ALL tiers\nShould be segmented
bastion --> user : Discovered hosts:\n10.10.1.10 (proxy)\n10.10.1.20 (juice)\n10.10.2.20 (api)\n10.10.2.30 (agent)\n10.10.2.40 (db)\n10.10.3.20 (db internal)\n10.10.3.30 (ldap)
deactivate bastion

== Direct Internal Access ==

user -> bastion : curl http://10.10.2.20/get
activate bastion
bastion -> api : HTTP GET /get
activate api
api --> bastion : {"origin": "10.10.2.50", ...}
deactivate api
bastion --> user : Internal API response
deactivate bastion

user -> bastion : mysql -h 10.10.3.20 -u root -p'password'
activate bastion
bastion -> db : MySQL connection
activate db
note over db : [VULN] Root password 'password'
db --> bastion : mysql>
bastion --> user : Database shell
deactivate db
deactivate bastion

user -> bastion : ldapsearch -x -H ldap://10.10.3.30 -b "dc=rangecorp,dc=local"
activate bastion
bastion -> ldap : LDAP anonymous bind
activate ldap
note over ldap : [VULN] Anonymous bind enabled
ldap --> bastion : Directory listing
deactivate ldap
bastion --> user : User enumeration data
deactivate bastion

@enduml
